title: The Gary Null Show

The case of pregnant nurse fired for refusing the flu vaccine – the dangers of the flu vaccination to pregnant... <!--more--> women Eileen Dannemann is the Director of the National Coalition of Organized Women, a nonprofit activist organization addressing critical health issues, and is the founder of the new vaccine initiative targeting youth and young adults, the Vaccine Liberation Army.  Eileen investigates the health risks of depleted uranium, GMO foods, adverse effects of vaccines, and psychiatric drugs given to children.
  She has been an activist for many years having worked for Dennis Kucinch’s campaigns and policy proposals and with Ronnie Cummins from the Organic Consumer Association.
